1467
02:12:25,270 --> 02:12:32,040
and put it into his pocket. He wrote a number
of short notes, one to Colonel Adye, and gave

1468
02:12:32,040 --> 02:12:33,920
them to his servant to take.

1469
02:12:33,920 --> 02:12:42,540
'There is no danger to you,' he said. He thought
for a time and then returned to his meal.

1470
02:12:42,540 --> 02:12:51,139
Finally he struck the table. 'We will have
him!' he said. 'He'll go too far.'

1471
02:12:51,139 --> 02:12:57,660
He went up to his room, carefully shutting
every door after him. 'It's a game,' he said,

1472
02:12:57,660 --> 02:13:03,800
'a strange game - but I shall win, Mr Griffin,'
he said.

1473
02:13:03,800 --> 02:13:11,020
He stood at the window staring at the hot
hillside. 'He must get food every day. Did

1474
02:13:11,020 --> 02:13:18,390
