somewhere? I wish we could get some good cold,

1475
02:13:18,390 --> 02:13:23,179
wet weather instead of the heat. He may be
watching me now.'

1476
02:13:23,179 --> 02:13:29,000
He went close to the window. Something hit
the wall above the window.

1477
02:13:29,000 --> 02:13:34,110
'I'm getting worried,' said Kemp. But it was
five minutes before he went to the window

1478
02:13:34,110 --> 02:13:39,530
again. 'It must have been a bird,' he said.

1479
02:13:39,530 --> 02:13:45,059
Soon he heard the front-door bell ringing
and hurried downstairs. He unchained and unlocked

1480
02:13:45,059 --> 02:13:50,139
the door, and opened it without showing himself.
It was Adye.

1481
02:13:50,139 --> 02:13:55,949
'Your servant's been attacked, Kemp,' he said
round the door.

1482
02:13:55,949 --> 02:13:58,210
'What!' exclaimed Kemp.

1483
02:13:58,210 --> 02:14:04,699
'She had that note of yours taken away from
her. He's very near. Let me in.'

1484
02:14:04,699 --> 02:14:10,190
Kemp opened the door a few inches, and Adye
came in. He stood in the hall, looking at

1485
02:14:10,190 --> 02:14:12,349
Kemp locking the door.

1486
02:14:12,349 --> 02:14:18,949
Kemp swore. 'What a fool I was!' he said.
'I might have known. Already!'

1487
02:14:18,949 --> 02:14:21,270
'What's the matter?' said Adye.

1488
02:14:21,270 --> 02:14:28,909
'Look here!' said Kemp, and led the way towards
his study. He handed Adye the Invisible Man's

1489
02:14:28,909 --> 02:14:29,909
letter.

1490
02:14:29,909 --> 02:14:34,329
Adye read it, 'And you-?' said Adye.

1491
02:14:34,329 --> 02:14:40,660
The sound of a breaking window came from upstairs.
Adye saw the little revolver half out of Kemp's

1492
02:14:40,660 --> 02:14:47,960
pocket. 'It's a window upstairs!' said Kemp,
and led the way up. There came a second noise

1493
02:14:47,960 --> 02:14:53,199
while they were still on the staircase. When
they reached the study they found two of the

1494
02:14:53,199 --> 02:14:59,440
three windows broken, the floor covered with
broken glass, and one big stone lying on the

1495
02:14:59,440 --> 02:15:06,770
writing table. The two men stopped in the
doorway. Kemp swore again, and as he did so

1496
02:15:06,770 --> 02:15:11,960
