1558
02:19:59,260 --> 02:20:06,880
air! Kemp did not hear the sound of the shot.
Adye raised himself on one arm, fell forward,

1559
02:20:06,880 --> 02:20:10,340
and lay still.

1560
02:20:10,340 --> 02:20:16,180
For a time Kemp remained looking at Adye as
he lay peacefully on the grass. The day was

1561
02:20:16,180 --> 02:20:24,510
very hot and still. Nothing seemed to move.
