asleep. Kemp's eyes returned to Adye - the

1564
02:20:37,160 --> 02:20:40,729
game was not beginning well!

1565
02:20:40,729 --> 02:20:45,981
Then came a ringing and a knocking at the
front door, but nobody opened it. Silence

1566
02:20:45,981 --> 02:20:52,040
followed. Kemp sat listening and then began
to look carefully out of the three windows,

1567
02:20:52,040 --> 02:20:58,010
one after another. He went to the stairs and
stood listening anxiously. What was his enemy

1568
02:20:58,010 --> 02:21:00,319
doing?

1569
02:21:00,319 --> 02:21:06,050
Suddenly there was a banging from below. He
waited and went down the stairs again. The

1570
02:21:06,050 --> 02:21:12,340
house was filled with the sound of heavy blows
