1576
02:21:39,979 --> 02:21:40,979
again.

1577
02:21:40,979 --> 02:21:47,380
'The Invisible Man!' said Kemp. 'He has a
revolver - with two shots left. He's killed

1578
02:21:47,380 --> 02:21:54,240
Adye. At least, he's shot him. Didn't you
see him on the grass? He's lying there.'

1579
02:21:54,240 --> 02:21:56,670
'Who?' said one of the policemen.

1580
02:21:56,670 --> 02:21:58,240
